2003-05-04  Marco Pesenti Gritti  <marco@it.gnome.org>

	* embed/mozilla/mozilla-embed-single.cpp:
	* embed/mozilla/mozilla-notifiers.cpp:
	* embed/mozilla/mozilla-notifiers.h:

